      "title": "CEB asks if the power cut can be reduced",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Public Utilities Commission of Sri Lanka has asked the Ceylon Electricity Board whether a reduction in the current power cut can be made as the disabled machine of the Norochchola thermal power plant has been connected to the national system again.",
        "The daily power cut extended to three hours as the first generator of the Norochchola power plant went down."
      ],
